# Google OAuth lo resuelve Firebase con: https://sistemicar-app.firebaseapp.com/__/auth/handler
# Si ves Error 500 en accounts.google.com, revisa en Google Cloud (proyecto sistemicar-app):
#   - OAuth client → Authorized JavaScript origins: http://localhost:5000 y http://127.0.0.1:5000
#   - OAuth client → Authorized redirect URIs: https://sistemicar-app.firebaseapp.com/__/auth/handler
# Firebase Console → Authentication → Settings → Authorized domains: localhost
